text: What Will You Do When You Catch Me? () is a 1978 Polish comedy movie directed by Stanisław Bareja and starring Kryzysztof Kowalewski, Bronisław Pawlik, Stanisław Tym, Ewa Wiśniewska, Ewa Ziętek, Stefan Friedmann. ==Other websites== * Category:1978 comedy movies Category:Polish comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Stanisław Bareja
title: What Will You Do When You Catch Me?
